WEBVTT

00:03.274 --> 00:05.206
Angie:
HEY, HONEY!

00:05.206 --> 00:06.537
HEY! WHAT ARE YOU GUYS
DOING HERE?

00:06.537 --> 00:08.439
BIRTHDAY DINNER,
REMEMBER?

00:08.439 --> 00:10.311
I´M KIDDING.
OF COURSE I REMEMBER.

00:10.311 --> 00:11.712
HAPPY BIRTHDAY,
SWEETHEART.

00:11.712 --> 00:14.285
[ SMOOCHES ]
I LOVE YOU.

00:14.285 --> 00:15.546
OH, THE PLACE CALLED,

00:15.546 --> 00:17.248
AND THE THING I GOT YOU
IS ON ITS WAY...

00:17.718 --> 00:20.751
FROM PARIS.

00:20.751 --> 00:23.294
IT´S NOT MY BIRTHDAY.

00:23.294 --> 00:25.326
WELL, THEN,
I´LL HOLD ON TO IT UNTIL...

00:25.326 --> 00:26.797
APRIL.

00:26.797 --> 00:28.199
[ SMOOCHES ]

00:28.199 --> 00:29.500
THAT´S YOUR BIRTHDAY.

00:29.500 --> 00:31.732
OOH, I WANT A NEW PUTTER --
YOU HEARD.

00:34.465 --> 00:37.037
DON´T TELL ME YOU
DON´T HAVE ANY IDEA

00:37.037 --> 00:38.509
WHOSE BIRTHDAY IT IS.

00:40.141 --> 00:42.773
[ Laughing ]
OF COURSE I DO.

00:46.077 --> 00:48.119
HAPPY BIRTHDAY, YOU!
[ GRUNTS ]

00:48.119 --> 00:50.581
IT´S GRANDMA´S BIRTHDAY.

00:50.581 --> 00:52.523
COME ON, ANGIE,
LAST YEAR,

00:52.523 --> 00:54.355
WHEN I SAID WE SHOULD GO OUT
FOR MY MOTHER´S BIRTHDAY,

00:54.355 --> 00:56.257
I MEANT SO THAT SHE
COULDN´T FIND US.

01:00.391 --> 01:02.733
GEORGE, HERE´S MY
LAST TIME CARD.

01:02.733 --> 01:05.136
OKAY, LET´S SEE
WHAT YOU DID LAST WEEK.

01:05.136 --> 01:06.797
YOU VANDALIZED THE FACTORY.

01:06.797 --> 01:09.800
YOU GAMBLED ON-LINE
WITH THE COMPANY CREDIT CARD.

01:09.800 --> 01:13.444
YOU SOLD A BAG OF OREGANO
TO SLOW BILL IN SHIPPING.

01:13.444 --> 01:15.306
SO, EVEN THOUGH YOU´RE
THE BOSS´S SON,

01:15.306 --> 01:17.178
YOU DON´T GET CRAP.

01:17.178 --> 01:19.680
WA-CHA!

01:19.680 --> 01:22.413
WELL, SINCE I´M NOT WORKING
WITH YOUR DAD ANYMORE,

01:22.413 --> 01:24.355
WHAT ARE YOU
DOING FRIDAY NIGHT?

01:24.355 --> 01:25.616
GOING OUT
WITH MY BOYFRIEND.

01:25.616 --> 01:27.318
I WOULD NEVER GO OUT
WITH SOME JERK

01:27.318 --> 01:28.819
WHO TRASHES THE PLACE
WHERE MY DAD WORKS.

01:28.819 --> 01:31.362
LOOK, DUDE,
SHE´S NOT GOING OUT WITH YOU

01:31.362 --> 01:32.663
AS LONG AS I´M ALIVE.

01:32.663 --> 01:34.495
WHEN DID YOU
GET A BOYFRIEND?

01:34.495 --> 01:37.428
I DON´T LIKE
THE SOUND OF THIS, GEORGE.

01:37.428 --> 01:39.770
WE HAVEN´T EVEN
MET THE BOY.

01:39.770 --> 01:41.632
OUT. COME ON.

01:41.632 --> 01:45.276
AW, GEORGIE,
NO KISS GOODBYE?

01:45.276 --> 01:48.309
YEAH, LET ME BEND OVER
AND DROP MY PANTS.

01:48.309 --> 01:50.541
FINALLY.

01:50.541 --> 01:52.783
SO, WHERE ARE WE GOING
FOR DINNER?

01:52.783 --> 01:54.885
SOMEPLACE QUIET
SO YOU CAN TELL US

01:54.885 --> 01:56.347
ABOUT YOUR NEW BOYFRIEND.

01:56.347 --> 01:57.788
I DON´T REALLY
HAVE A NEW BOYFRIEND.

01:57.788 --> 01:59.890
I WAS JUST SAYING THAT
SO HE´D LEAVE ME ALONE.

01:59.890 --> 02:01.592
IF YOU DON´T
HAVE A BOYFRIEND,

02:01.592 --> 02:03.894
THEN WHO WERE YOU TALKING TO
ON THE PHONE LAST NIGHT?

02:05.456 --> 02:07.328
[ Imitating Carmen ]
"I´M ONLY A GOOD KISSER

02:07.328 --> 02:08.759
´CAUSE I´M KISSING YOU."

02:08.759 --> 02:11.562
[ SMOOCHING ]

02:13.133 --> 02:16.907
I CAN´T WAIT UNTIL YOU FINALLY
GET YOUR FIRST GIRLFRIEND.

02:16.907 --> 02:21.172
MY KIDS ARE GONNA LOVE
WALKING IT AND FEEDING IT.

02:21.172 --> 02:24.545
SO YOU ARE PREGNANT?!

02:24.545 --> 02:25.646
BUTT-MUNCH.

02:25.646 --> 02:27.278
BUTT-WEED.
BUTT-FACE.

02:27.278 --> 02:31.882
YOU´RE BOTH BUTT-MUNCHING,
BUTT-WEEDING BUTT-FACES.

02:31.882 --> 02:35.926
CARMEN, WHY DIDN´T YOU TELL US
YOU WERE SEEING SOMEONE?

02:35.926 --> 02:38.158
WELL, BECAUSE IT´S TOO EARLY
FOR YOU GUYS TO MEET HIM.

02:38.158 --> 02:40.491
WHEN I WAS DATING JASON,
YOU AND DAD WERE ALL OVER US.

02:40.491 --> 02:41.832
IT WAS IMPOSSIBLE.

02:41.832 --> 02:43.594
BUT LOOK, CARMEN,
YOU´RE STILL 15, OKAY?

02:43.594 --> 02:45.396
YOU CAN´T DATE ANYONE
UNLESS WE MEET HIM.

02:45.396 --> 02:46.797
HEY, AND THAT´S MY PHONE.

02:48.399 --> 02:50.170
HEY, HAPPY BIRTHDAY TO ME.

02:50.170 --> 02:52.843
LET´S GET THIS DINNER
OVER WITH. COME ON.

02:52.843 --> 02:54.575
HOW OLD ARE YOU,
GRANDMA?

02:54.575 --> 02:56.277
HOW OLD WAS I
LAST YEAR?

02:56.277 --> 02:58.309
NONE OF MY STINKIN´ BUSINESS.

02:58.309 --> 03:01.252
OH, YOU REMEMBERED.

03:08.259 --> 03:09.960
IT WAS TOO SOON
TO BRING NOAH HERE.

03:09.960 --> 03:10.961
DAD´S GONNA MESS IT UP.

03:10.961 --> 03:12.593
CARMEN, RELAX.

03:12.593 --> 03:15.426
YOUR DAD JUST WANTED A FEW
MINUTES TO GET TO KNOW HIM.

03:15.426 --> 03:17.298
A FEW MINUTES?

03:17.298 --> 03:19.230
IT ONLY TOOK HIM FIVE SECONDS
TO CONVINCE MY LAST BOYFRIEND

03:19.230 --> 03:21.272
THAT I WAS BORN
WITHOUT A TONGUE...

03:22.573 --> 03:25.806
AND THAT THIS
WAS A DONOR FROM A COW.

03:27.608 --> 03:29.440
WELL, CONGRATULATE ME.

03:29.440 --> 03:32.513
I JUST FINISHED
MY LAST HISTORY TEST.

03:32.513 --> 03:34.515
YOU´VE BEEN IN CLASS
THIS WHOLE TIME?

03:34.515 --> 03:36.747
IT´S 6:00. I THOUGHT YOU
WERE AT SOCCER PRACTICE.

03:36.747 --> 03:39.550
NO, THE TEACHER LET ME STAY
A LITTLE LONGER TO FINISH.

03:39.550 --> 03:41.952
HEY, DID YOU KNOW
THAT THE CLASSROOM LIGHTS

03:41.952 --> 03:43.424
GO OUT AUTOMATICALLY

03:43.424 --> 03:45.556
IF YOU DON´T MOVE
FOR 20 MINUTES?

03:47.758 --> 03:49.730
SO HOW´D YOU DO?

03:49.730 --> 03:52.263
WHO WROTE THE DECLARATION
OF INDEPENDENCE?

03:52.263 --> 03:54.265
THOMAS JEFFERSON.

03:54.265 --> 03:56.337
SERIOUSLY?

03:59.009 --> 04:01.312
WELL, UH, NOW WE WAIT.

04:03.474 --> 04:05.476
WHAT COULD THEY
BE TALKING ABOUT?

04:05.476 --> 04:07.578
CARMEN, YOUR FATHER´S
OLD-FASHIONED.

04:07.578 --> 04:10.551
I´M SURE HE WANTS TO KNOW
WHAT NOAH´S INTENTIONS ARE.

04:10.551 --> 04:14.024
YOU GOT YOUR BUN WARMER,
EXTRA BURNER,

04:14.024 --> 04:15.986
TEMPERATURE GAUGE, HUH?

04:15.986 --> 04:18.258
ROTISSERIE ATTACHMENT...

04:18.258 --> 04:19.960
DID I NEED IT? NO.

04:19.960 --> 04:21.662
DO I USE IT? NO.

04:21.662 --> 04:25.035
HAPPY I GOT IT?
YOU BET YOUR ASS.

04:25.035 --> 04:27.668
THE STEAKS
LOOK PERFECT.

04:27.668 --> 04:28.939
YOU KNOW, SON,

04:28.939 --> 04:31.842
THE T-BONE ISN´T
AN EASY STEAK TO GRILL.

04:31.842 --> 04:36.677
´CAUSE IT´S ACTUALLY
TWO STEAKS IN ONE.

04:38.309 --> 04:40.411
THAT´S RIGHT.

04:40.411 --> 04:41.712
I WAS DRIVING BY,

04:41.712 --> 04:43.754
I SAW THE SMOKE,
I GOT WORRIED.

04:43.754 --> 04:46.817
I THOUGHT YOU MIGHT
BE HAVING STEAKS WITHOUT ME.

04:48.919 --> 04:50.521
YOU MUST BE GRANDMA BENNY.

04:50.521 --> 04:52.292
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?

04:52.292 --> 04:54.965
THIS IS NOAH,
CARMEN´S NEW BOYFRIEND.

04:54.965 --> 04:57.798
CARMEN´S TOLD ME A LOT
OF NICE THINGS ABOUT YOU.

04:57.798 --> 05:00.401
YEAH? NAME ONE.

05:00.401 --> 05:03.934
SHE SAYS YOU CAN MIX YOUR
OWN MARGARITAS IN YOUR MOUTH.

05:10.941 --> 05:12.343
WELL, YEAH.

05:12.343 --> 05:13.884
YOU KNOW,
WHEN YOU´RE BABYSITTING,

05:13.884 --> 05:18.689
YOU HAVE TO FIND WAYS
TO AMUSE THE KIDS.

05:18.689 --> 05:20.951
HEY, NOAH, CAN YOU HELP ME
SET THE TABLE?

05:20.951 --> 05:24.495
SURE, SURE, YEAH.
EXCUSE ME, EXCUSE ME.

05:27.798 --> 05:31.532
TWO CUTE BOYFRIENDS
IN A ROW.

05:32.833 --> 05:34.505
YOU KNOW WHAT?

05:34.505 --> 05:37.468
MAYBE I SHOULD START WEARING
MY JEANS REAL LOW LIKE THAT.

05:39.570 --> 05:41.011
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

05:41.011 --> 05:42.573
OH, LOOK, MOM,

05:42.573 --> 05:46.617
IT´S ALL OF AMERICA
CALLING TO ASK YOU NOT TO.

05:46.617 --> 05:49.950
I BETTER GIVE THIS
TO NOAH. OH.

05:49.950 --> 05:51.452
WHAT IS IT?

05:51.452 --> 05:52.923
IT´S A TEXT MESSAGE.

05:52.923 --> 05:55.386
"LET ME KNOW
WHEN YOU GET RID OF CARMEN.

05:55.386 --> 05:58.659
CAN´T WAIT
TO SEE YOU TONIGHT."

05:58.659 --> 06:00.561
HE´S CHEATING
ON MY DAUGHTER.

06:00.561 --> 06:03.994
WELL, IT´S LIKE MY MOTHER
ALWAYS SAID TO ME --

06:03.994 --> 06:07.097
"GET CHEATED ON ONCE,
SHAME ON THEM.

06:07.097 --> 06:10.971
GET CHEATED ON TWICE...
START PUTTING OUT."

06:13.073 --> 06:15.706
[ INTRO TO WAR´S "LOW RIDER"
PLAYS ]

06:26.417 --> 06:32.693
♫ ALL MY FRIENDS
KNOW THE LOW RIDER ♫

06:32.693 --> 06:37.928
♫ THE LOW RIDER
IS A LITTLE HIGHER ♫

07:03.694 --> 07:06.697
MRS. LOPEZ,
YOUR COOKING IS DELICIOUS.

07:06.697 --> 07:08.629
THANK YOU.

07:08.629 --> 07:10.430
YOU´RE SO SWEET.

07:10.430 --> 07:13.564
YOU KNOW, WE STILL HAVE
SOME CORN AND BEANS LEFT.

07:13.564 --> 07:14.705
I´LL HAVE A LITTLE
OF BOTH.

07:14.705 --> 07:16.737
OF COURSE YOU WILL.

07:20.741 --> 07:22.643
YOU´RE NOT HAPPY
WITH JUST CORN.

07:22.643 --> 07:24.014
NO, NOT YOU, MAN.

07:24.014 --> 07:25.876
YOU GOT TO HAVE A LITTLE BEANS
ON THE SIDE.

07:28.919 --> 07:30.180
YOU HAD BETTER BE CAREFUL.

07:30.180 --> 07:32.182
SOME NIGHT YOU´RE
GONNA BE EATING BEANS,

07:32.182 --> 07:34.725
AND YOU´RE GONNA
GET ALL SCREWED UP AND SAY,

07:34.725 --> 07:36.687
"I LOVE YOU, CORN."

07:38.929 --> 07:41.061
WHAT ARE YOU GUYS
TALKING ABOUT?

07:41.061 --> 07:43.033
LOOK, I´M JUST SAYING...

07:45.836 --> 07:50.541
LOOK, I MADE A COMMITMENT
TO CORN 17 YEARS AGO.

07:50.541 --> 07:51.872
SURE, I´M A MAN.

07:51.872 --> 07:53.744
SOMETIMES I LIKE
TO GO TO A BARBECUE

07:53.744 --> 07:54.905
AND SEE BEANS I LIKE.

07:56.206 --> 08:00.711
BAKED BEANS, RED BEANS,
BLACK BEANS...

08:00.711 --> 08:03.954
BIG, PLUMP GARBANZOS.

08:03.954 --> 08:07.658
BUT, NO,
I ALWAYS COME HOME

08:07.658 --> 08:10.490
TO MY SWEET,
SWEET CORN.

08:12.623 --> 08:15.666
GEORGE, BENNY...

08:15.666 --> 08:17.167
THE "CORN" NEEDS A WORD.

08:25.976 --> 08:28.278
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING?

08:28.278 --> 08:30.280
ANGIE, HE´S
CHEATING ON CARMEN.

08:30.280 --> 08:31.912
HOW DO YOU KNOW?

08:31.912 --> 08:34.284
WE SAW HIS CELLPHONE.
HE GOT A TEXT MESSAGE --

08:34.284 --> 08:36.847
"LET ME KNOW WHEN YOU CAN
GET RID OF CARMEN.

08:36.847 --> 08:38.749
CAN´T WAIT
TO SEE YOU TONIGHT."

08:38.749 --> 08:40.220
OKAY, THAT
SOUNDS SUSPICIOUS,

08:40.220 --> 08:42.793
BUT YOU KNOW WHAT?
IT COULD MEAN A LOT OF THINGS.

08:42.793 --> 08:44.595
IT COULD BE A GIRL
WHO´S A FRIEND

08:44.595 --> 08:47.297
OR A COUSIN WHO HASN´T
SEEN HIM IN A LONG TIME.

08:47.297 --> 08:50.861
YOU JUST GOT THE GREEN LIGHT
FOR SIDE ACTION

08:50.861 --> 08:53.133
BECAUSE SHE WILL NEVER
FIGURE IT OUT.

09:00.540 --> 09:02.873
OKAY, LOOK, ANGIE, MY DAUGHTER
JUST GOT HER HEART BROKEN

09:02.873 --> 09:04.615
BY A GUY
THAT CHEATED ON HER, OKAY?

09:04.615 --> 09:06.216
I´M NOT GONNA STAND BY
AND DO NOTHING.

09:06.216 --> 09:08.949
HONEY, WE ALMOST RUINED HER
LAST RELATIONSHIP

09:08.949 --> 09:10.751
BY INTERFERING TOO MUCH.

09:10.751 --> 09:12.983
I DON´T THINK
THAT WE SHOULD DO ANYTHING

09:12.983 --> 09:14.685
UNTIL WE KNOW FOR SURE.

09:14.685 --> 09:17.758
I KNOW FOR SURE
THAT GUY´S A LIAR.

09:17.758 --> 09:19.089
HOW?

09:19.089 --> 09:21.862
HE SAID YOUR COOKING
WAS DELICIOUS!

09:23.634 --> 09:25.565
WHAT?

09:27.167 --> 09:31.041
EITHER HE´S A LIAR
OR HE´S NEVER HAD FOOD BEFORE.

09:32.703 --> 09:34.204
NOAH´S
GOT TO TAKE OFF.

09:34.204 --> 09:36.046
Noah: YEAH, I GOT AN EARLY
SWIM PRACTICE TOMORROW.

09:36.046 --> 09:40.110
OH, I HOPE MR. LOPEZ
DIDN´T SCARE YOU AWAY.

09:40.110 --> 09:42.012
YOU KNOW, CARMEN´S
BEEN THROUGH A LOT LATELY,

09:42.012 --> 09:43.754
AND HE´S BEING
A LITTLE OVERPROTECTIVE.

09:43.754 --> 09:46.586
I COMPLETELY UNDERSTAND.

09:46.586 --> 09:51.061
MR. LOPEZ, I PROMISE
I WILL TREAT CARMEN RIGHT.

09:51.061 --> 09:53.794
I WILL ALWAYS
BE STRAIGHT WITH HER.

09:53.794 --> 09:55.966
I WILL NEVER,
EVER HURT HER.

09:57.197 --> 09:58.799
IT WAS NICE
MEETING EVERYONE.

09:58.799 --> 10:00.370
THANK YOU SO MUCH
FOR DINNER.

10:00.370 --> 10:01.832
YOU´RE WELCOME.

10:01.832 --> 10:03.804
SEE YA.

10:03.804 --> 10:05.175
BYE.

10:05.175 --> 10:06.907
[ SQUEALS ]

10:11.341 --> 10:12.683
SO?

10:12.683 --> 10:14.845
SEEMS LIKE
A NICE KID TO ME.

10:14.845 --> 10:16.146
YOU KNOW WHAT?
YOU´RE RIGHT.

10:16.146 --> 10:17.888
I GUESS I
COULD LEARN FROM YOU

10:17.888 --> 10:19.790
AND NOT ALWAYS
THINK THE WORST OF PEOPLE.

10:19.790 --> 10:22.292
OH, HONEY.

10:22.292 --> 10:23.854
[ SMOOCHES ]

10:27.928 --> 10:29.229
GET YOUR CAR.

10:29.229 --> 10:32.262
WE´RE GONNA
FOLLOW THAT LITTLE MAGGOT.

10:34.164 --> 10:36.707
I DID NOT NEED A CAR
TO CATCH YOUR FATHER CHEATING.

10:36.707 --> 10:39.169
I JUST WENT KNOCKING
ON THE NEIGHBORS´ DOORS

10:39.169 --> 10:41.371
UNTIL SOMEONE
LOOKED SURPRISED.

11:01.261 --> 11:04.034
HEY, THIS IS THE BIGGEST TUB
OF POPCORN

11:04.034 --> 11:05.335
I´VE EVER SEEN,

11:05.335 --> 11:08.038
AND IT STILL DOESN´T
COVER YOUR HEAD.

11:15.045 --> 11:16.847
He´s obviously here
to meet a girl.

11:16.847 --> 11:19.309
No guy comes to see
"A Walk In The Tuscan Meadow"

11:19.309 --> 11:20.680
by himself.

11:20.680 --> 11:23.683
Man, guys will
do anything to get some.

11:23.683 --> 11:26.116
Oh, it´s not that bad.
I saw it with Angie last week.

11:29.389 --> 11:30.861
Ding! Ding! Ding!

11:30.861 --> 11:32.993
My ho-dar´s going off.

11:34.694 --> 11:35.966
Oh, he is cheating!

11:35.966 --> 11:40.130
Boy, too bad
this isn´t an action movie.

11:40.130 --> 11:42.302
We could use
some explosions

11:42.302 --> 11:45.435
to cover his screams
when we kick his butt.

11:45.435 --> 11:47.778
Don´t worry, Mom, there´s plenty
of noise when the farm girl

11:47.778 --> 11:49.740
gives birth to the cheesemaker´s
kid in the barn.

11:49.740 --> 11:54.214
There´s a little nudity,
but it does get tastefully done.

12:04.795 --> 12:06.726
Did you see that?

12:06.726 --> 12:07.998
I saw!
I saw!

12:07.998 --> 12:09.259
Kiss that guy?

12:11.201 --> 12:13.003
Man, that kid´s
a player.

12:13.003 --> 12:15.165
He´s just playing
for the other team.

12:17.237 --> 12:19.810
Shh!
Have some respect!

12:33.884 --> 12:36.987
MAX, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING UP?

12:36.987 --> 12:38.388
I CAN´T SLEEP.

12:38.388 --> 12:40.961
YOU KNOW, IF I FAILED
THAT HISTORY TEST,

12:40.961 --> 12:42.893
I WON´T PASS
THE FIFTH GRADE.

12:42.893 --> 12:44.935
[ SIGHS ] HONEY...

12:44.935 --> 12:47.137
YOUR DAD AND I
TALKED ABOUT THIS.

12:47.137 --> 12:50.070
WE KNOW THAT YOU´VE
WORKED HARD ALL YEAR,

12:50.070 --> 12:51.771
AND YOU´VE DONE YOUR BEST.

12:51.771 --> 12:55.245
IF YOU GET HELD BACK,
YOU´LL STILL BE ALL RIGHT.

12:55.245 --> 12:57.247
A LOT OF FAMOUS PEOPLE

12:57.247 --> 12:59.910
NEVER EVEN FINISHED
ELEMENTARY SCHOOL.

12:59.910 --> 13:02.512
UM, CHARLES DICKENS...

13:02.512 --> 13:04.384
MARK TWAIN...

13:04.384 --> 13:07.317
THOMAS EDISON.

13:07.317 --> 13:10.560
HOW ABOUT SOMEONE
I´VE HEARD OF?

13:13.994 --> 13:15.065
MAX, IT´S LATE.

13:15.065 --> 13:17.467
GO TO BED, SON.

13:20.971 --> 13:22.332
WHERE HAVE
YOU TWO BEEN?

13:22.332 --> 13:24.935
OKAY, ANGIE, YOU´RE
NEVER GONNA BELIEVE THIS.

13:24.935 --> 13:28.208
WE FOLLOWED NOAH TO SEE IF HE
WAS CHEATING ON CARMEN.

13:28.208 --> 13:30.340
GEORGE, YOU´RE
GONNA RUIN CARMEN´S CHANCES

13:30.340 --> 13:31.541
WITH THIS GUY.

13:39.249 --> 13:41.221
THE ONLY CHANCES
CARMEN HAS

13:41.221 --> 13:43.123
IS IF SHE
GETS A BUZZ CUT

13:43.123 --> 13:46.356
OR SHE STARTS
PACKING SOME SOCKS.

13:50.100 --> 13:51.862
ANGIE...

13:51.862 --> 13:53.103
HE´S GAY.

13:55.505 --> 13:57.007
HOW DO YOU KNOW?

13:57.007 --> 13:58.568
WELL, WE FOLLOWED HIM,

13:58.568 --> 14:01.111
AND HE WENT TO SEE "A WALK
IN THE TUSCAN MEADOW."

14:03.113 --> 14:05.245
THAT DOESN´T
MEAN HE´S GAY.

14:05.245 --> 14:07.247
I KNOW ONE GUY WHO SAW IT

14:07.247 --> 14:09.479
JUST TO GET HIS WIFE
IN THE MOOD,

14:09.479 --> 14:11.281
AND THEN ALL THROUGHOUT
THE MOVIE,

14:11.281 --> 14:12.622
HE KEPT NUDGING HER --

14:12.622 --> 14:15.225
"ARE YOU READY YET?
ARE YOU READY YET?"

14:16.386 --> 14:19.990
"WOW, THAT WAS A TRIUMPH
OF THE HUMAN SPIRIT!

14:19.990 --> 14:21.591
ARE YOU READY YET?"

14:23.193 --> 14:26.136
LOOK, ANGIE,
WE SAW HIM KISSING A DUDE.

14:28.899 --> 14:30.870
ARE YOU SURE?

14:30.870 --> 14:33.243
OH, YES.

14:35.105 --> 14:36.947
IT COULDN´T HAVE BEEN
A FRIENDLY PECK ON THE CHEEK

14:36.947 --> 14:38.148
LIKE THEY DO IN EUROPE?

14:38.148 --> 14:40.250
LOOK, I´VE
NEVER BEEN TO EUROPE,

14:40.250 --> 14:43.984
BUT IF IT´S FILLED WITH GAY
TEENAGE BOYS TONGUE WRESTLING,

14:43.984 --> 14:46.116
THEN, YEAH,
IT WAS LIKE THAT.

14:47.988 --> 14:49.519
THIS IS GONNA
KILL CARMEN.

14:49.519 --> 14:50.890
I KNOW.
WHERE IS SHE?

14:50.890 --> 14:52.362
