WHAT NOAH MUST BE FEELING.

15:07.237 --> 15:09.139
WELL, I DON´T
HAVE TO IMAGINE.

15:09.139 --> 15:11.111
I SAW WHAT
HE WAS FEELING.

15:15.115 --> 15:16.947
IT WAS MUSCULAR
AND 17...

15:16.947 --> 15:18.048
MOM!

15:32.632 --> 15:34.104
MORNING.

15:34.104 --> 15:36.236
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?
MY DAD´S STILL HOME.

15:36.236 --> 15:38.168
I WANTED TO
TAKE YOU TO SCHOOL.

15:38.168 --> 15:39.569
