SHE WAS SEEING ZACK.

19:53.363 --> 19:54.424
ZACK?

19:54.424 --> 19:55.725
ZACK POWERS?

19:55.725 --> 19:58.568
[ Chuckles nervously ]
UM, ACTUALLY...

19:58.568 --> 20:00.700
WAIT, WAIT,
WAIT, WAIT!

20:00.700 --> 20:02.732
SHE WAS SEEING ZACK POWERS
BEHIND OUR BACK,

20:02.732 --> 20:04.203
