20:04.203 --> 20:06.336
LOOK, I´M REALLY SORRY
ABOUT THIS.

20:06.336 --> 20:08.678
I MEAN, YOU GUYS
WERE SO NICE TO ME.

20:08.678 --> 20:10.740
I REALLY ENJOYED
MEETING YOUR MOTHER.

20:10.740 --> 20:13.343
ENOUGH OF YOUR LIES!
OUT!

20:15.685 --> 20:17.287
"I ENJOYED
MEETING YOUR MOTHER"?

20:17.287 --> 20:19.989
THAT LOCO! "I ENJOYED
MEETING YOUR MOTHER"!

20:21.691 --> 20:24.754
I KNOW I´VE SAID THIS A LOT,
BUT THIS TIME I MEAN IT.

20:24.754 --> 20:27.727
I AM GONNA KILL CARMEN.

20:27.727 --> 20:30.900
