OF YOU NOT INCLUDING ME

20:30.900 --> 20:34.764
WHEN IT COMES
TO PARENTING.

20:34.764 --> 20:37.937
WE ARE GONNA KILL CARMEN.

20:37.937 --> 20:39.939
SO WE´LL
HAVE ONE KID LEFT.

20:39.939 --> 20:42.772
MAX IS A GOOD BOY.
